<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-indent:21pt;"><span><font face="Times New Roman">2</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">、由中国日报社与日本言论</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">NPO</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">共同主办的第八届北京</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">—</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">东京论坛</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">7</font></span><span
