face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">4</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日</span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">访问罗马尼亚罗康斯坦察港，军舰高级军官代表分别拜会了罗海军舰队司令和康斯坦察县议会主席等当地军政官员，并专程前往位于罗首都布加勒斯特的海军总部，拜会罗海军参谋长奥雷尔？波帕中将等罗海军主要领导人。这是中罗建交</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">63</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年来中国军舰首次到访罗马尼亚。</span></p>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-indent:21pt;"><span><font face="Times New Roman">7</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">、国家食品药品监管局日前发布《加强药用辅料监督管理的有关规定》。《规定》明确了药品生产企业、药用辅料生产企业、监管部门各自的职责，明确了药用辅料的监管模式，并设立了信息公开、延伸监管、社会监督等工作机制。</span></p>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-indent:21pt;"><span><font face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">、日前，农业部、财政部联合印发了《</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">2012</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">年农产品产地初加工补助项目实施指导意见》。安排</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">5</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">亿元资金，专门用于农产品产地初加工补助项目的实施。通过财政</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">以奖代补</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">、部门指导、技术培训等综合措施，支持农户和专业合作社建设产地初加工设施，推广普及科学适用的初加工技术。</span></p>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-indent:21pt;"><span><font face="Times New Roman">9</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">、</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">6</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">日</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">，中国首艘</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">300</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">米</span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">饱和潜水母船</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">深潜号</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">在青岛建造竣工并交付交通运输部使用。</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">深潜号</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">总长</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">125.7</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">米</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">，型宽</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">25</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">米</span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">，型深</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">10.6</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">米</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">，满载排水量</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">15864</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">吨。</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">深潜号</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的最大亮点是配置了一套</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">300</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">米</span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">饱和潜水系统，最大工作深度可达水下</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">300</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">米</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span></p>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-indent:21pt;"><span><font face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">、中国资深外交官吴红波</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">6</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">日</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">在纽约联合国总部正式宣誓就任联合国负责经济和社会事务的副秘书长，坦言就任后要做好</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">三个转变</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span></p>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-indent:10.5pt;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">　</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">11</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">7</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日，国土资源部副部长胡存智在京表示，近</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">3</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年以来，国土资源部门实现了保障性安居工程用地应保尽保。去年共落实用地</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">4.36</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万公顷，今年计划安排供应土地</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">4.76</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万公顷，为年度测算需求的</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">1.76</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">倍，目前已落实</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">2</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万多公顷。</span></p>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-indent:21pt;"><span><font face="Times New Roman">12</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">、《重大节假日免收小型客车通行费实施方案》对社会公布。今后，春节、清明节、劳动节、国庆节等</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">4</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">个国家法定节假日，以及当年国务院办公厅文件确定的上述法定节假日连休日，免收</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">7</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">座及以下小型客车通行费。免费通行的收费公路范围为符合《中华人民共和国公路法》和《收费公路管理条例》规定，经依法批准设置的收费公路（含收费桥梁和隧道）。各地机场高速公路是否实行免费通行，由各省（区、市）人民政府决定。</span></p>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-indent:21pt;"><span><font face="Times New Roman">13</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">、</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">日</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">，中国稀土产品交易所有限公司在被誉为</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">稀土之都</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的内蒙古包头市正式揭牌成立。这是包钢稀土、厦门钨业等</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">家稀土生产和流通骨干企业，每家出资</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">1000</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">万元成立的国内首个稀土产品交易平台。专家认为，此举将有助于增强市场透明度，增强我国对稀土产品定价的话语权，维护稀土市场稳定。</span></p>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-indent:21pt;"><span><font face="Times New Roman">14</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">、我国科学家潘建伟等人近期在国际上首次成功实现百公里量级的自由空间量子隐形传态和纠缠分发，为发射全球首颗</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">量子通讯卫星</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">奠定技术基础。量子信息因其传输高效和绝对安全等特点，被认为可能是下一代</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">IT</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">技术的支撑性研究，并成为全球物理学研究的前沿与焦点领域。中科院于</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">2011</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年启动了空间科学战略性先导科技专项，力争在</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">2015</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年左右发射全球首颗</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">量子通讯卫星</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span></p>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-indent:21pt;"><span><font face="Times New Roman">15</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">、从</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">2012</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">年起，中央财政将</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">普通高中改造计划</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">实施范围从西部集中连片特殊困难地区扩大到中西部集中连片特殊困难地区。中央财政近日下达补助资金</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">20</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">亿元，支持中西部集中连片特殊困难地区普通高中校舍改扩建、图书和教学仪器设备配置、体育运动场等附属设施建设，不得用于人员经费和偿还债务等方面。</span></p>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-indent:21pt;"><span><font face="Times New Roman">16</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">、卫生部新闻发言人邓海华在今天召开的新闻发布会上指出，《预包装食品营养标签通则》将于</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">2013</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">1</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">1</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日</span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">正式施行，标志着我国全面推行食品营养标签管理制度，强制标示能量和</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">4</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">种营养成分的含量值及参考值。</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">17</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">日</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">，国家营养标签健康教育行动计划在京启动。今后</span><span><font
face="Times New Roman">3</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年，我国将开展以贯彻营养标签为主题的教育行动，并对食品企业进行营养标签知识指导。</span></p>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-indent:21pt;"><span><font face="Times New Roman">17</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">、全国</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span
