<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-indent:21pt;"><span><font face="Times New Roman">26</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">、科技部：</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">2011</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">年我国在全球最有影响力也就是被引用次数居于前</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">1%</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">的论文（即</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">高被引论文</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span
style="font-family:宋体;">）数量已跃居世界第</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">6</font></span><span
